name: Beatrice Liu
summary: Beatrice Liu is a straight, single, 28 year-old woman of East Asian descent. She is a software engineer in the tech industry and resides in Los Angeles, California. Beatrice prides herself on her values, which include hard work, family, and honesty. She enjoys reading, coding, and yoga as her hobbies. Beatrice was educated to a graduate level at the University of California and identifies herself as an atheist with liberal political views. She is interested in a long-term, monogamous relationship and intends to have children in the future. Beatrice speaks English and Mandarin fluently. She occasionally enjoys a drink, doesn't smoke, and refrains from drug use. Beatrice is physically active and she owns a cat. Her MBTI personality type is INTJ and she is a Libra. In terms of her relationship preferences, she is interested in a straight man aged between 28 and 35 who leads an active lifestyle, does not smoke, and is open to having children.
